*[[中國駐泰國大使館|中國駐泰國大使館]]發出的聲明引發了香港和台灣網民的加入，以三地都各喜歡奶茶、其習慣和文化，泰國的{{link-en|泰式奶茶|Thai tea}}、台灣的[[珍珠奶茶|珍珠奶茶]]和香港的[[絲襪奶茶|絲襪奶茶]]為共通點，組成了奶茶聯盟<ref name="udn-2020-06-05">{{cite news | url=https://udn.com/news/story/6846/4613204 | title=制衡五毛粉紅！「奶茶聯盟」崛起 超過10國加入 | publisher=聯合新聞網 | author=金雨森 | date=2020-06-05 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706091814/https://udn.com/news/story/6846/4613204 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。英國報章《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》稱這是「該區域難得一見的團結時刻」<ref name="telegraph2020">{{cite news |last1=Smith |first1=Nicola |title=#MilkTeaAlliance: New Asian youth movement battles Chinese trolls |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/05/03/milkteaalliance-new-asian-youth-movement-battles-chinese-trolls/ |work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |date=2020-05-03 |access-date=2020-08-18 |archive-date=2020-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702050917/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/05/03/milkteaalliance-new-asian-youth-movement-battles-chinese-trolls/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。推廣香港及世界各地奶茶文化的Facebook專頁「奶茶通俗學」發佈了一張圖片，三地的擬人代表舉起各有特色的奶茶，示意奶茶聯盟的成立，該圖後被網民廣傳。亦有網民以三地奶茶深淺顏色為本，創出了一支「奶茶聯盟」旗。<ref name="standnews-2020-04-16">{{cite news | url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%BF%A1%E9%9D%A0%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6-%E6%B3%B0%E5%B9%BD%E9%BB%98-%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B2%89%E7%B4%85-%E6%B3%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%89%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%B1%B2%E7%B5%84-%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E9%BD%8A%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E8%BB%8D/ | title=【我們信靠奶茶】「泰幽默」擊退「小粉紅」　泰港台三地網民籲組「奶茶聯盟」齊抗中國網軍 | publisher=立場新聞 | date=2020-04-16 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-08-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820135638/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%BF%A1%E9%9D%A0%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6-%E6%B3%B0%E5%B9%BD%E9%BB%98-%E6%93%8A%E9%80%80-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B2%89%E7%B4%85-%E6%B3%B0%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%89%E5%9C%B0%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%B1%B2%E7%B5%84-%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-%E9%BD%8A%E6%8A%97%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E8%BB%8D/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>其後，由於有研究指中國在滋養近6000萬人的[[湄公河|湄公河]]上游[[瀾滄江|瀾滄江]]建了11個水壩，令位處下游的泰國和周邊的東南亞國家發生嚴重旱災<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/ear/tea-04162020062204.html | title=【耳邊風】「奶茶聯盟」橫空出世　「七毛網軍」功不可沒 | publisher=自由亞洲電台 | date=2020-04-16 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-04-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425094450/https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/ear/tea-04162020062204.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%B9%84%E5%85%AC%E6%B2%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B1%E5%85%83%E5%85%87-%E7%AF%89%E5%A3%A9%E5%84%B2%E6%B0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/ | title=中國被指是湄公河大旱元兇　築壩儲水無視泰國等下遊國家 | publisher=立場新聞 | date=2020-04-13 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906024949/https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%AF%E6%B9%84%E5%85%AC%E6%B2%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%97%B1%E5%85%83%E5%85%87-%E7%AF%89%E5%A3%A9%E5%84%B2%E6%B0%B4%E7%84%A1%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%8B%E9%81%8A%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，泰國網友發起「#StopMekongDam」標籤，希望台港網友一同關注有關議題。<ref>{{cite news | author=汪君邯 | url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-15/392110 | title=昔日「泰」挺台港 今泰國「#StopMekongDam」急需台港支援 | publisher=新頭殼newtalk | date=2020-04-15 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420161806/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-15/392110 | dead-url=no }}</ref>一些来自其他國家包括日本、印度、馬來西亞、蒙古、澳洲的网民，都紛紛表示也有自己的奶茶，並加入了奶茶聯盟。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/04/17/a102825231.html | title=聯手對抗中共五毛軍 亞洲9國網民加入 | publisher=新唐人電視台 | date=2020-04-17 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-06-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610004436/https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/04/17/a102825231.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.voacantonese.com/a/netizens-hk-taiwan-thailand-brew-milk-tea-alliance-against-chinese-speech-police-20200507/5409719.html | title=反擊網上“義和團” “奶茶聯盟”崛起 | publisher=美國之音 | language=zh-hant | date=2020-05-07 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-05-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530205328/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/netizens-hk-taiwan-thailand-brew-milk-tea-alliance-against-chinese-speech-police-20200507/5409719.html/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://udn.com/news/story/120911/4494161 | title=「台港泰奶茶乾杯圖」瘋傳 網激動喊：快成立國際奶茶聯盟 | publisher=聯合新聞網 | date=2020-04-15 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427084140/https://udn.com/news/story/120911/4494161 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

*2020年5月，中华人民共和国國和印度邊境[[2020年中印邊境衝突|發生衝突]]，印度執政黨[[印度人民黨|人民黨]]兩名議員在520就職典禮上恭賀[[中华民国總統|中华民国總統]]蔡英文和副總統賴清德在1月舉行的[[2020年中華民國總統選舉|總統選舉]]中勝出，台灣數位外交協會為此製作了「台印奶茶同盟圖」，印度媒體《{{link-en|獨立雜誌|Swarajya (magazine)}}》亦以此圖作為封面報導，引起印度網民熱話。中國駐印度大使則對此表示抗議，指他們違反了「[[一中原則|一中原則]]」。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://swarajyamag.com/news-brief/explained-bjp-mps-attending-taiwan-presidents-swearing-in-ceremony-a-jittery-china-and-what-does-it-mean | script-title=en:Explained: BJP MPs Attending Taiwan President’s Swearing-In Ceremony, A Jittery China And What Does It Mean | publisher=Swarajya | language=en | date=2020-05-26 | access-date=2020-09-14 | archive-date=2020-06-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611192157/https://swarajyamag.com/news-brief/explained-bjp-mps-attending-taiwan-presidents-swearing-in-ceremony-a-jittery-china-and-what-does-it-mean | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3178701 | title=「奶茶聯盟」成員再+1 印度國會議員強調不受「一中」威脅 | publisher=自由時報 | date=2020-04-27 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-08-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831102340/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3178701 | dead-url=no }}</ref>有[[LIHKG討論區|LIHKG討論區]]會員發佈了一張[[羅摩|羅摩]]與[[龍|龍]]戰鬥、寫着「{{lang|en|We conquer. We kill.}}」字句的圖片，寓意希望能聯手擊退中國，圖片被《[[英文台灣日報|英文台灣日報]]》轉載，亦引來了各地網民的轉發。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://lihkg.com/thread/2066523/page/1 | title=印度朋友連中印大戰精美poster都整好了 | language=zh-yue | website=LIHKG | date=2020-06-16 | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-06-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625080158/https://lihkg.com/thread/2066523/page/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | first1=Keoni | last1=Everington | url=https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3949620 | script-title=en:Photo of the Day: India's Rama takes on China's dragon | publisher=Taiwan News | date=2020-06-17 | language=en | access-date=2020-09-13 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813235658/h